snippet.title: OWN
snippet.description:
OWN: Oprah Winfrey Network is the first and only network named for, and inspired by, a single iconic leader. Oprah Winfrey's heart and creative instincts inform the brand -- and the magnetism of the channel.

Visit http://www.oprah.com/own to learn more about Queen Sugar, David Makes Man, Greenleaf, Iyanla: Fix My Life, SuperSoul Sunday, Ambitions, Family or Fiance, and other OWN shows. 

Subscribe to OWN's YouTube channel and see below for our upload schedule from our lineup. Be sure to like, comment and share the videos with your friends. Be a part of the conversation and subscribe today!
